  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Demonstrate that a 4-day training session will allow nurses to master basic hypnoanalgesia
      techniques, and this new tool will translate into a reduction of procedural distress and pain
      in their patients, thereby opening the way to larger clinical trials in various pediatric
      settings.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
